    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable driver at a lower price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading paint on the roof, and a few small dings along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, and while the engine runs steadily, it will likely need a routine tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has served us well but definitely shows the signs of regular use over the years.",
