    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an impeccable standard that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a showroom-quality aesthetic, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. This is an investment-grade example of automotive excellence, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
