      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute dream of a car, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014it\u2019s in pristine condition and drives like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here! I\u2019m only letting it go because our family is growing, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person!",
